CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1951, pg. 10 reads: " Mrs. Jesse T. Henderson - Harris Photo." Portion of accompanying article reads: "Mary Amanda Bussey, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. James Bussey of Singer Place, was married on Sept. 1 at Trinity AME Church to Jesse T. Hendersosn [Henderson] Jr., son of Mr. and Mrs. Jesse T. Henderson, Amsterdam, N.Y."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two men and two women, possibly Mr. and Mrs. James Bussey and Mr. and Mrs. Jesse T. Henderson, posed in home of Mr. and Mrs. James Bussey, Singer Place
